item.title: CVE-2022-22301|2024-08-03T03:07:50.235Z -- fortinet -- fortinet%20fortiap-c
item.description: An improper neutralization of special elements used in an OS Command vulnerability [CWE-78] in FortiAP-C console 5.4.0 through 5.4.3, 5.2.0 through 5.2.1 may allow an authenticated attacker to execute unauthorized commands by running CLI commands with specifically crafted arguments.
